"{\"uid\": \"cnn.com-2024-08-15-sport-raygun-olympic-bullying-petition-intl-spt-index.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Follow:  The AustralianOlympicCommittee (AOC) has condemned an anonymous online petition concerning Rachael Gunn - the viral breaker known asRaygun- saying it contains falsehoods about how she was selected to compete at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, a 36-year-old university lecturer from Sydney, failed to register a point in her battles against USA's Logistx, France's Syssy and Lithuania'sNicka, losing 18-0 on each occasion.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9997886652725864, \"rank\": 0.00012942095594267738, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 283, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999679766921, \"rank\": 1.906187248565673e-08, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8435179049218204, \"rank\": 0.1855112868920811, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, her performance ignited widespread social media commentary and critique.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related articleAustralian breaker Raygun earns mixed reviews, praised for 'courage' and 'character' after viral performances at Paris Games  In a statement on Thursday, the AOC's Chief Executive Officer Matt Carroll criticized the \\\"vexatious, misleading and bullying\\\" petition that \\\"contains numerous falsehoods designed to engender hatred against an athlete who was selected in the Australian Olympic Team through a transparent and independent qualification event and nomination process.\\\"\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 542, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.796407494927517e-24, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.5824490752954454, \"rank\": 0.7168882953282617, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 711, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Carroll_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.9257385252729587, \"rank\": 0.053658536585363466, \"text\": \"Matt Carroll\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Carroll_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Carroll_(basketball)\"}, {\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999288681946, \"rank\": 7.11318803936882e-08, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The petition, published on Sunday and addressed to Australian Prime MinisterAnthony Albaneseand the AOC, was posted to Change.org.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9992200823658315, \"rank\": 0.0005528590022051155, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.5824490752954454, \"rank\": 0.7168882953282617, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Change.org\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It alleges - without evidence - that Gunn \\\"manipulated\\\" the selection process, \\\"raising serious questions about the fairness and integrity of the process.\\\"\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9997886652725864, \"rank\": 0.00012942095594267738, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also alleges that Gunn's husband could have been part of the selection panel and calls for Gunn and Australia's Olympic chef de mission Anna Meares to apologize for \\\"misleading the Australian public and attempting to gaslight the public and undermining the efforts of genuine athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9997886652725864, \"rank\": 0.00012942095594267738, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9997886652725864, \"rank\": 0.00012942095594267738, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1390, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9490025994740575, \"rank\": 0.05340532485060302, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}, {\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9992200823658315, \"rank\": 0.0005528590022051155, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn said in anInstagram videothat she did not realize her performance would \\\"open the door to so much hate, which has frankly been pretty devastating.\\\"\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9997886652725864, \"rank\": 0.00012942095594267738, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I really appreciate the positivity and I am glad I was able to bring some joy into your lives - that's what I hoped.\\\"\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carroll said the AOC has written to Change.org demanding that the petition be immediately withdrawn.\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1863, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\", \"score\": 0.9994248864227993, \"rank\": 0.00028540463987857624, \"text\": \"Carroll\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DeMarre_Carroll\"}, {\"begin\": 1880, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.5824490752954454, \"rank\": 0.7168882953282617, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Change.org\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The AOC is particularly offended by the affront to our Chef de Mission, Anna Meares,\\\" said Carroll.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.5824490752954454, \"rank\": 0.7168882953282617, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/